            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "We have been associated with Kunskapsskolan for past 5 years and now our daughter is in Grade 3 … An I must express my heartfelt gratitude to entire Kunskapsskolan team and all the teachers who have been so supportive towards the idea of making our kids independent and letting them express their selves by demonstrating their skill sets … The School completely justifies the Name KUNSKAPSSKOLAN (Knowledge School) the knowledge of self worth and self confidence and team work …\n\nThanks once again and my special thanks to\nMs.Cinderella Bose , Ms.Asiya Bedi , Ms.Parul Sharma , Ms.Akanksha Sharma , Ms.Ankita Kapur and Ms.Bipasha Roy who have lent their extended support in all matters when it comes to our kids growth …\n\nLooking forward to many years of association and joyful times together .",
          "publisher": {
            "@type": "Organization",
            "name": "Yellow Slate"
          }
