          "reviewBody": "I've been teaching in this should since the last 3 years. It's an amazing place built upon a lot of values and strives upon perfection. The way the school supports and stands by it's teachers is truly amazing.\nMoreover if you have your child studying here, there isn't a thing a parent needs to sorry about as we strive upon making the child an independent learner, not only when it comes to academics but also when it comes to skills that a person would require life long!\nKunskapsskolan Gurgaon is the best CBSE school one should be in: whether as a student or as a teacher!",
